Mitigation Control:
Apply data minimization principles; collect only job-relevant information;
 conduct a GDPR Data Protection Impact Assessment (DPIA);
 enforce secure data retention and deletion policies.

Evaluate model performance across different job 
categories and demographic groups;
establish minimum accuracy and fairness thresholds before deployment.

Require human review for high-impact or borderline decisions;
 establish a formal candidate appeals process;
 continuously monitor rejection trends.
